<title>
CAN-communicatiecontrole
</title>
<ptxt>
Voer met behulp van het SUZUKI-uitleesapparaat &#34;Communicatiestoring-DTC&#34; onder &#34;Buscontrole&#34; uit en controleer de DTC&#39;s van alle regelapparaten die met de CAN-communicatiebus zijn verbonden.
</ptxt>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "3" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "2.854in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "2.854in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "1.457in"/>
<thead>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Toestand
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Actie
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Referentie
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
In elk van de systemen werden alleen vroegere DTC&#39;s waargenomen
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Controleer de DTC opnieuw na het wissen van de DTC en het uitvoeren van de rijtest. Als de controleresultaten in orde zijn, gaat het om een sporadische storing.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
In elk van de systemen werd &#34;Bus regelapparaat uitgeschakeld&#34; waargenomen (huidige DTC)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Voer &#34;Storingzoeken bij communicatiebus uit&#34; uit
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ADUAP70AA804004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
In elk van de systemen werd alleen &#34;Verbroken communicatie&#34; waargenomen (huidige DTC)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Voer &#34;Storingzoeken voor verbroken communicatie&#34; uit
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "ADUAP70AA804003"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Geen weergave op het SUZUKI-uitleesapparaat (het is niet mogelijk om met alle systemen te communiceren.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle">
<ptxt>
Controleer of het SUZUKI-uitleesapparaat kan communiceren door het op een ander voertuig aan te sluiten.
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
—
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
